 support future wind development opportunities across Canada and specifically in Atlantic Canada.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Paris\u00e9, Jason", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Walker, Tony R.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8ec45425632fa669a0feccfd64351a74", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/55408ec73feaa3e0c719c1adf037aaca5bb58727409a1967216f09f6a3450a10", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/44CMSK35", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/44CMSK35", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/3cf8cf6d4422a48b3df9e0e20b645940!/b208156-210634", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "252-259", "title": "Journal of Environmental Management", "volume": "201"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8ec45425632fa669a0feccfd64351a74"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:44CMSK35"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.jenvman.2017.06.052"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13437634"}}]}}, "title": "Industrial wind turbine post-construction bird and bat monitoring: A policy framework 